Every user sees the same number of ads, the difference being that those who consent to processing personal data will see much more interesting offers. Without this consent, you will regularly see ads for online games, quick loans or some other mostly irrelevant banners. On top of that, it will be much harder to promptly respond to any potential problems with the app.
By exiting the Consent Manager Provider you accept to give your personal data to all purposes and vendors.
Listonic needs to collect some data like device identifier to make sure that we can track any problems that can occur while using the application. It helps us fix things faster.

Listonic personalizes your advertising experience. Our partners may collect and process personal data such as the device identifier, location data, and other demographic and interest data to provide advertising experience tailored to you. By agreeing to this improved ad experience, you’ll see ads that are more relevant to you. If you do not consent, you will still see ads, but they may be not relevant to you at all.

With respect to the new European law, depending on the features you use, we may process a variety of information about you, including personal data and information about your Listonic activities for the purpose of providing the Services, improving the functionality of Listonic and for marketing purposes. In the next step, you can choose which data we

We protect all information about you. Remember that you can always exercise the rights granted to you by the GDPR in particular the right of access to data, objection and withdrawal of consent to Cookies. You will find all details in the Listonic Privacy Policy
